      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "Precarious weak layers exist in the snowpack on northwest, north and northeast facing slopes. <br/> The weather conditions as the day progresses will give rise to increasing moistening of the snowpack in some places in particular on steep slopes below approximately 2700 m. The new snow will be deposited on a weakly bonded old snowpack below approximately 2700 m."
